# Badge

[Previous](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/radix/avatar)
[Next](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/radix/breadcrumb)
Displays a badge or a component that looks like a badge.
[Radix UI](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/radix/badge)
[Base UI](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/base/badge)

```
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/badge" export function BadgeDemo() {
```


